{"tid":1770831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩同啲fd打邊爐比人打","createTime":"2019-12-05T11:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T12:54:01.000Z","uid":238801,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab333abb8eb6d0af771f9d65d106bd52da9bb20","tid":1770831,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:56:58.000Z","msg":"好火，話說今日見天氣涼左，咁咪約班friend出泥打邊爐，<br />\n去到間鋪前，我地見到班mk，本身我地都直行直過，無理佢<br />\n但班mk就唔知點解啤住曬，又口upup咁<br />\n<br />\n好啦，咁我地坐低坐，落曬order，咁咪吹下水囉<br />\n<br />\n直至D野泥曬喇，依班mk開始泥料<br />\n果時我第一個淥野食既，班mk無啦啦一拳中埋泥<br />\n我班friend o曬咀，D腸仔蛋係個口跌曬出泥<br />\n咁我緊係即刻捉住條mk屌佢做嘜打我<br />\n點知條mk無啦啦講左句 淥野先中<br />\n我r曬頭，即刻屌柒佢睇話劇死返去文娛中心啦<br />\n<br />\n可能班mk班friend知驚，佢地即刻跑走曬<br />\n留低左小mk,而我就捉左依個小mk比差佬 <br />\n打個爐無啦啦俾人打，痴線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ff281b6d24ec36b70bccfff18c9009851b3f42","tid":1770831,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"read."},{"pid":"64277a4cbad9eead77d5bea48a346b3bb53fe430","tid":1770831,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"woho"},{"pid":"def15e06e1abe6191e1585b9dda752060628fabe","tid":1770831,"uid":85219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Cc0FhD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Cc0FhD.gif&h=c151aa5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66afb63b0f7571810d2b6fa007491b41427da392","tid":1770831,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64277a4cbad9eead77d5bea48a346b3bb53fe430","tid":1770831,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"woho"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"wohooo"},{"pid":"41f23902aab5e2b3eaf63e83df01fc956ce75191","tid":1770831,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66afb63b0f7571810d2b6fa007491b4